  allLines:
  - side: 1
    characterName: Ary
    characterSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ece41423a199ba04f8804d355c231cbb, type: 3}
    sentence: "I think it\u2019s good to hold onto some childish tendencies such
      as get-to-know you activities. We aren\u2019t as different from our younger
      selves as we think. "
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Loreen
    characterSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 146a6ce1894c7084984f7771ba7e263e, type: 3}
    sentence: That is very true. Most of our traits are just more complex versions
      of the ones we had in our childhood.
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Ary
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: You must have been a well-spoken kid, then.
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Loreen
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: Says you. I must say, you are very close to wooing me with your incredible
